self.cmd = (
    """%(pgm)s %(in_fqfn)s
                         -d ','
                         --fieldcnt 7
                         --quoting 'quote_none'
                         --outgood %(outgood)s
                         --outerr  %(outerr)s
                         --validschema %(schema)s
                   """
     % {'pgm': self.pgm, 'outgood': self.outgood_fqfn, 'outerr': self.
    outerr_fqfn, 'in_fqfn': self.std_7x7_fqfn, 'schema': self.schema_fqfn})
print(self.cmd)
runner = envoy.run(self.cmd)
self.get_outputs(runner)
print(self.std_out)
print(self.std_err)
print(self.err_output)
assert self.status_code == 0
assert not self.err_output
assert len(self.good_output) == 7
assert not self.std_out
assert not self.std_err or len(self.std_err
    ) < 50 and 'Coverage.py' in self.std_err
